CustomField.description: The API name of a field set used by the Methodology object. Fields in this field set define the editable fields in the Methodologies section of the Create Project from Template page. The default value is CreateProjFromTemplateMethodologyColumns.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: API name of a field set used by the Methodology object. Fields in this field set define the editable fields in the Methodologies section of the Create Project from Template page.
CustomField.label: Template Proj Meth Fieldset
